                    technical documents.
homepage            https://typeof.net/Iosevka/

distfiles           ttf-${name}-${version}.zip

checksums           rmd160  87907e2075220eeebf7a90321476eb2ef718bd8e \
                    sha256  5ea8abdbd7204ecd163994def636a5182787cfa8b9349af9c1ffa27cd868a905 \
